section.section:
Nine (9) of the members shall be volunteers and shall be appointed by the Governor from a list of nominees in the following manner:
Three (3) of the appointed members shall represent family members of persons with a disability;
Two (2) of the appointed members shall be persons with a disability;
One (1) of the appointed members shall represent professionals and providers of services to persons with a disability;
One (1) of the appointed members shall represent advocates for persons with a disability; and
Two (2) of the appointed members shall represent the community at large.
